{"data":[{"author":"Braci Ltd.","capabilities":[],"category_id":"5261a8fb3b773043d5000004","category_name":"Health & Fitness","category_color":"98D500","changelog":[],"companions":{"ios":null,"android":{"id":"54a6813d2daaa4f4bc000053","icon":"https://www.filepicker.io/api/file/lsEVxwTDKOFCFnTXkhZQ","name":"Braci - On The Go","url":"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ugs.onthego","required":true,"pebblekit_version":"3"}},"compatibility":{"ios":{"supported":false},"android":{"supported":true},"aplite":{"supported":true,"firmware":{"major":2}},"basalt":{"supported":false,"firmware":{"major":2}},"chalk":{"supported":false,"firmware":{"major":2}},"diorite":{"supported":true,"firmware":{"major":2}},"emery":{"supported":false,"firmware":{"major":2}}},"created_at":"2015-01-02T11:29:31.274Z","description":"Braci – ‘On The Go’ is a unique application that is used by people who are continuously on the go and out & about cycling, driving or just having a walk while listening to music through their headphones. The application detects and alerts users to sounds happening in their environments, including car horns, sirens (police, ambulance, and fire engines) train whistles and traffic tones. \r\nThe sound is detected through the microphone of the user’s smartphone, once the sound is detected, any type of music playing will automatically pause and the user will be notified through a series of vibrations and on screen event, occurring on both a smartphone and smartwatch. All of this process occurs within 1-2 seconds, making the application have a very fast responsive time.\r\nFeatures:\r\n\r\n1- Highly sensitive and accurate \r\n2- Smart Notification – Stopping music to allow the user to pay attention\r\n3- Internationally Universal – comes pre-installed with car horn sounds\r\n4- Noise Cancellation – Cancelling out all other outdoor background sounds","developer_id":"52c1799a01696bf4a7000050","header_images":[{"orig":"https://assets.getpebble.com/api/file/exU5U0SpSZ